edu.cmu.sei.arche.vo
Class QuestionToUserVO

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.sei.arche.vo.CoreFact
      edu.cmu.sei.arche.vo.QuestionToUserVO
public class QuestionToUserVO
extends CoreFact

Corresponds to a question that ArchE wants to ask to the user. Maps to fact MAIN::AskQuestion. Further information about a question is found in the questions bundle properties file.

Author:
Paulo Merson
